New grouped chronogram

new_grouped_chronogram.Rd

A constructor for a grouped chronogram. This is called automatically by the S3 method: group_by.cg_tbl().

Usage

new_grouped_chronogram(x, groups, ..., class = character())

Arguments

x

a chronogram

groups

groups

...

parsed to dplyr::group_by()

class

character vector of class

Value

an extended grouped tibble with class grouped_cg_df
